{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Felfele Foundation","author":"Mark Vujevits"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eb1054f2-a354-5af0-b202-e6d5f7b5695b","excerpt":"We are back from Swarm Orange Summit Madrid edition, where we presented about how we use Ethereum Swarm to build a fully decentralized…","html":"<p>We are back from Swarm Orange Summit Madrid edition, where we presented about how we use Ethereum Swarm to build a fully decentralized, mobile-first social application.</p>\n<p>Swarm Orange Summit is a yearly gathering where the core Swarm team and members of the community present about their work, and discuss the possible futures of the technology. If you are interested in decentralization, and you haven’t heard about Swarm yet, you should head to their <a href=\"https://ethswarm.org\">website</a> to learn about an incentivised p2p storage network! This year Epic Labs hosted the event in their Madrid office. Kudos to them for making it happen!</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"attila present\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-b0c9e.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-f36df.jpg 125w,\n/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-4a0b6.jpg 250w,\n/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-b0c9e.jpg 500w,\n/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-8a2fd.jpg 750w,\n/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-219ba.jpg 1000w,\n/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-35975.jpg 1500w,\n/static/attila-present-dce0e4b07d0d60cb9a97c0cd04416276-6a121.jpg 4032w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>From the Felfele team Attila Gazso took the stage to <a href=\"https://prezi.com/qhpiczkatr-r\">present</a> about the current stage of our project. He talked about the motivation for building social network and the challanges we face. He introduced to the community the social APIs we build, which enables any application developer to interface with the social network. To demonstrate it, we built a <a href=\"https://github.com/felfele/felfele/tree/master/src/cli\">command line tool</a> to post updates and query data.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"mighty wallet\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-b0c9e.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-f36df.jpg 125w,\n/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-4a0b6.jpg 250w,\n/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-b0c9e.jpg 500w,\n/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-8a2fd.jpg 750w,\n/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-219ba.jpg 1000w,\n/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-35975.jpg 1500w,\n/static/mighty-wallet-9535fb9773e66523a11b9725dd6b81bc-45988.jpg 3264w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>We hosted a lottery during the summit, where anyone could apply by <a href=\"https://felfele.org/donate\">donating</a> to the foundation. It was an exceptional present: a Mighty Wallet hand-drawn by our director of design, David. It’s a one of a kind item, and the happy winner was <a href=\"https://twitter.com/terepauto\">Adam Schmideg</a>, from the Ethereum Foundation, congrats!</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 500px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 133.33333333333331%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"wallet winner\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-b0c9e.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-f36df.jpg 125w,\n/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-4a0b6.jpg 250w,\n/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-b0c9e.jpg 500w,\n/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-8a2fd.jpg 750w,\n/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-219ba.jpg 1000w,\n/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-35975.jpg 1500w,\n/static/wallet-winner-2ceffd94b3637651898183990e373088-49e58.jpg 3024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>Continue the conversation on twitter</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet tw-align-center\" data-lang=\"en\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Read a recap of our time at <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/SwarmOrangeSummit?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#SwarmOrangeSummit</a> recently in Madrid! Videos of presentations to come! <a href=\"https://t.co/Y0pPT6xTEO\">https://t.co/Y0pPT6xTEO</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%24MFT&amp;src=ctag&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">$MFT</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/buidl?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#buidl</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/eth?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#eth</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/blockchain?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#blockchain</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/cryptocurrency?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#cryptocurrency</a></p>&mdash; Mainframe (@Mainframe_HQ) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Mainframe_HQ/status/1138839820363415552?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">June 12, 2019</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>","frontmatter":{"title":"Felfele ❤️ Swarm Orange Summit","date":"June 03, 2019","path":"/blog/sos/"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/sos/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/sos/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/manual-1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Felfele User Manual 1.0.0","path":"/blog/manual-1/"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/swarmhackweek2019/brainstorming/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Swarm Hack Week 2019 Brainstorming","path":"/blog/swarmhackweek2019/"}}}}